(38437, '1', '0', 'ZUNI! NOOOO!', '14', '0', '100', '0', '0', '0', ''),
(38437, '2', '0', 'I\'ll send some watchers ta get his body so we can offer a proper farewell... I wish I could do more.', '12', '0', '100', '0', '0', '0', ''),
(38437, '3', '0', 'I\'m afraid there\'s nothin\' I can do for our brother... her power tore away at his soul.', '12', '0', '100', '0', '0', '0', ''),
(38437, '4', '0', 'Vol\'jin rushed off in eagerness, but I can take us back to safety. Just give me the word when ya ready, mon.', '12', '0', '100', '0', '0', '0', '');
